title: Inclusion & Access  Craft & Cozy
description: Join the Inclusion & Access Committee for a relaxed craft night with snacks and tea! It will be on Thursday, February 23 from 4:00 - 6:00 PM. We'll have various crafts to keep your creativity flowing, so come on down and chill with us.

title: Bowling & Indian Bites
description:
More Info!
Join Basic Needs Hub, Food Pantry, International Student Office, Resource Center for Students with Children, and ASPSU Global Community! This Thursday from 2:00 - 4:00 we will share Indian food to comfort Indian students, the most significant international student population, with domestic students who might enjoy different cultural cuisine. Get to know everyone by creating a space to share food and play games together, and hopefully come together as a big Portland State Family!

title: Virtual Game Night
description: Game with us this Thursday from 4:00-6:00 PM through Zoom! Inclusion & Access is hosting a game night, so if you're a homebody who wants to make friends, get involved! We'll have a ton of different games and opportunities to connect with different peers and members of the Inclusion & Access Committee! Click Below to save the Zoom Link or more info.
